Replace this comment with a 'generic ble out' node.

Install: npm install node-red-contrib-generic-ble

Configure the BLE node with your GATT characteristic UUID.
The payload is a Buffer containing compact JSON:
  {"t":"ABN","c":"abnormal","p":85,"ts":1234567890}
  {"t":"OK","p":95,"ts":1234567890}
